    <content>&lt;P&gt;See my blog about how I did this:&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-builders-blog-posts/how-to-scrape-images-from-google/ba-p/13941824" target="_blank"&gt;https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-builders-blog-posts/how-to-scrape-images-from-google/ba-p/13941824&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Let me know what you think.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":grinning_cat_face:"&gt;😺&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
